Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明与黑暗\N在陷入一片混乱的战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了四魂之玉\N因缘际会聚在一起的伙伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越五百年的时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后仅存的四魂之玉碎片\N引导着各自的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.57,0:00:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传说故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.94,0:00:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.54,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣大人的真实身分果然是桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.41,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追踪死魂虫而去的我\N终于见到了桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.62,0:00:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗  你还活着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.12,0:00:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You Can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.36,0:00:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a world（暧昧的世界）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.13,0:00:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋力冲出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.84,0:00:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对忧郁的现实生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.78,0:00:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在心中自我成长的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.65,0:01:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜的梦境及梦中残留的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断断续续提醒我“勇往直前”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.03,0:01:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破茧而出的我  及含苞待放的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.80,0:01:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就将它禁锢起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.81,0:01:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You Can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.24,0:01:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.84,0:01:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go in and try（不顾一切的去尝试）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.25,0:01:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.32,0:01:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你天长地久永不分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.82,0:01:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to Cry（同样的哭泣）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.22,0:01:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孤独相伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me a day fight（直接应战）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.12,0:01:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当伤心流泪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.39,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它成为坚定不移的梦想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是要我跟去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第151话\N戈薇本能的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的人都死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产房里的人全部都死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听第二天早上\N发现这件事的大人说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉的那些人状况都非常奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是妖怪下的毒手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好夫人跟刚刚出世的小少爷\N都没有出事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.06,0:03:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是佛祖保佑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子  真是个乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.14,0:03:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经加强了城中的戒备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是妖怪还是什么敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都休想靠近这个城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天好不容易\N恩赐给我的继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用自己的生命来保护他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是我生下来的孩子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.93,0:04:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个白衣女童只是幻影吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.37,0:04:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.58,0:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我还真不想变老呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是一点点的柴而已\N我竟然背不起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这样勉强自己是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子  你叫什么名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你的名字啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚有地方去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不嫌弃的话就来我家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几顿饭我还招待得起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字还真特别啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.82,0:04:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚\N这好像是最后一个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母也出了不少力喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道还有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.49,0:05:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  连这个地方也有妖怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.86,0:05:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吓我们好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇她去追死魂虫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追死魂虫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就突然不见踪影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看那个地方\N可能是结界之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个结界在什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.81,0:05:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经即将走到尽头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且瘴气还在不断蔓延当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘴气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你做一个选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出手相救还是不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗她怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在白灵山魔塌之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被奈落用毒触手贯穿身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠入了瘴气的浊流之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.99,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于\N她的身体是由灵骨和墓土合成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此当时并没有被瘴气溶化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就算是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.93,0:06:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从伤口侵入的瘴气\N已经蔓延渗透到全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在胸前的伤口\N还是无法愈合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且进一步正在腐蚀当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在唯一能救她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你一个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人能够救桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正掌握着她的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要我做一个选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.97,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做才能够救桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择救她吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有我能够救她吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.21,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要触摸她一下就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来瘴气就会被净化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要触摸一下就可以了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这具灵魂附体的人偶\N已经遭到破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要让灵魂停留在体内\N变得更加困难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不赶在日落之前净化瘴气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人的灵魂就会完全消散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些水让人好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是奈落的瘴气\N渐渐的渗出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就是溶化出来的瘴气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是从桔梗的体内泄出来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  让我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.61,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说只要触摸一下\N就可以了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样才能够让桔梗醒过来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个人的墓土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你的手\N已经净化了那些墓土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它填到胸前的伤口处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓土被瘴气顶出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘴气的力量随着夜晚的降临\N将不断增强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不赶在日落之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救回那个人的灵魂的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.54,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是要被弹开一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片漆黑  什么都看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…四魂之玉\N好像太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.53,0:10:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.43,0:10:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的是桔梗死前的场景吗\N犬夜叉这家伙睡过头了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是五十年前发生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用这个来化妆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙的本性也不会变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个胭脂根本就不适合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用妖怪的血\N来妆点自己就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.97,0:10:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  这不是犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉怎么可能会说出这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.52,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从头到尾从来都没有想过\N要成为愚蠢的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你没有发现呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.59,0:11:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉我就不客气地收下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.13,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个玉还得要再多吸取一些\N仇恨的鲜血才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗  这家伙是奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把村里的人都杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.37,0:11:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.67,0:11:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你没有发现吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的灵魂已经渐渐消散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇就是从这里消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里  你在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.68,0:11:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗肩膀跟胸前的伤口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟现在伤在同一个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么的相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枉费我是这么的相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然对我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  桔梗姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.86,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听好  小枫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个东西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个四魂之玉\N跟我的尸体一起烧掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.60,0:12:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.23,0:12:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能让它再落入\N邪恶之徒手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗的灵魂被困在这个时空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.51,0:13:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.88,0:13:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.01,0:13:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…\N桔梗的时间停止的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  我到底是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我做了一个梦吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦  什么样的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在脑子里一片模糊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口在愈合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点点  加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.33,0:13:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他真的很想再见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你一定要撑下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.14,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.41,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也很想再见到犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.19,0:14:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…变清澈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘴气已经被净化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好…了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.52,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死魂虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.13,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N是你呼唤我来的不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该可以做选择的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要救我还是不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是选择不选择的问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己面前\N有一个可以得救的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又被告知\N只有我一个人可以救的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然是非救不可不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就不谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是你的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人的脾气也真是有够别扭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.28,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在水中看到了什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得的话  那就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他马上就会来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是来追你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会暂时躲起来一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我必须蓄积自己的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不去见犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.28,0:16:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.95,0:16:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他\N自从听到了圣大人的传闻之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个人满脑子\N就只想着你一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.46,0:16:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉想见到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很不是滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快点走吧\N说不定结界已经解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请做一个选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要救她还是不救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.99,0:17:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.99,0:17:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的好像是在试探人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.60,0:17:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  为什么要这么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗以为我会把她看成是障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而认定我不会救她吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是难道\N而是就只有这种可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N居然把我当成那种小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.01,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的把我看成\N是那种讨厌的女人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.69,0:17:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.02,0:17:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.93,0:17:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在东张西望什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗她已经走了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去追她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗刚才在这个地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不过她已经走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我有劝她跟你见一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.45,0:18:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去追吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.30,0:18:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚跟桔梗发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候\N我拼了命的想要救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到现在却是这样的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.84,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.01,0:18:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊\N从刚刚开始就在闹什么情绪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.66,0:18:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做错了什么事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.89,0:18:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不讲清楚的话\N我也要生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.90,0:18:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道整个来龙去脉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想应该是犬夜叉不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.54,0:19:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然戈薇都这么说了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看戈薇那个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那么落寞的样子\N以前从来都没有看过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉\N我觉得我还要先问问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去追桔梗姑娘\N真的没有关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看戈薇那个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能去追啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.63,0:19:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说如果\N戈薇笑嬉嬉地让你去追的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会飞奔而去咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人生闷气\N又迁怒到犬夜叉的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他已经开始讨厌我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.19,0:19:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在生气吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去追桔梗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我一个人在山脚下的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有遇见圣大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.68,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过\N那只是桔梗所操纵的纸人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.62,0:20:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的桔梗\N听说被奈落的瘴气所侵蚀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经生命垂危了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.79,0:20:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候是什么样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她受了伤一直在沉睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘴气已经被净化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她现在应该已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.61,0:20:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你帮她净化瘴气的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很担心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你快去追她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要有所顾虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.73,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是不要再勉强自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已经救回桔梗了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样那就没有关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会去追她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…没有关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N你要收回刚才说的那句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.21,0:21:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要说你忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是说\N你最讨厌我了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有…说过那种话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.55,0:21:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我已经忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.22,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这句话\N让我受到多大的打击啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他很在意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小气鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.80,0:21:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候\N戈薇的心里没有任何的犹豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她有所迟疑的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.77,0:21:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我胸前的这个伤口\N就没有办法愈合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在都还暖暖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.29,0:22:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New World 全新梦想的起点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.26,0:22:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向目标持续旅程 直到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.30,0:22:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New Mind 怀抱热情直到下一扇门扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.54,0:22:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲向未知的世界 快奔驰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.12,0:22:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手触摸 那微尘般的希望之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.82,0:22:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使勉强握住 横冲直撞的我们想往何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.53,0:22:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保有自我 Let's go and Try 前进吧 使命只有One way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.61,0:23:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺其自然 Do it!Ready? 最后愿望将达成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.85,0:23:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New World 全新梦想的起点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.82,0:23:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向目标持续旅程 直到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.86,0:23:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New Mind 怀抱热情直到下一扇门扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.14,0:23:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲向未知的世界 快奔驰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.56,0:23:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在圣大人出现的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.29,0:23:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿毘公主的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.29,0:23:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到有个妖怪不攻击的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.63,0:23:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要杀了奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.90,0:23:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从跟那个家伙有所瓜葛之后\N就没有什么好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.33,0:23:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制妖鸟向那个地方\N发动攻击的阿毘公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.97,0:23:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保卫城堡的人群中\N出现了琥珀的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.97,0:23:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像以前\N也曾经像这样战斗过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.47,0:24:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的伙伴一起同心协力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.51,0:24:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护并且夺取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.08,0:24:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  你要保护那个婴儿



